title.narrative: Vietnam Livestock Competitiveness and Food Safety

description.narrative: The project development objectives (PDOs) are to increase the production efficiency of household-based livestock producers, to reduce the environmental impact of livestock production, processing and marketing, and to improve food safety in livestock product supply chains (mainly meat) in selected provinces.
